  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Place the Norwegian Mozzarella Balls in a single layer on a baking sheet.",
    "Bake for 12-15 minutes, or until the mozzarella is golden brown and slightly shattery.",
    "Meanwhile, place the earthenware bowl in the oven to warm up for 5-7 minutes.",
    "Remove the bowl from the oven and place the baked mozzarella balls inside.",
    "Garnish with fresh thyme and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Serve immediately, while the mozzarella is still warm and shattery."
